<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Sugar1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Sugar,</orth> subst. the sweet substance made from Saccharum officinarum: <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.231" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 231</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.3.31" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 3, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.3.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 3, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.3.6" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 3, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.126" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 126</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.25" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.25" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 25</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.25" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 25</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.242" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 242</bibl>. Adjectively, == sweet: <cit><quote>severed lips, parted with s. breath,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.119" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 2, 119</bibl></cit>. <emph>there is more eloquence in a s. touch of them</emph> (your lips) <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.303" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 303</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>